or management reporting purposes jpmorgan chases activities are organized into a corporateprivate equity segment and four business segments consumer and community banking corporate and investment bank commercial banking and asset management the investment banking division at jp morgan is divided by teams industry ma and capital markets industry teams include consumer and retail healthcare diversified industries and transportation natural resources financial institutions metals and mining real estate and technology media and telecommunications jpmorgan europe ltdedit main article jp morgan in the united kingdom the company known previously as chase manhattan international limited was founded on september   in august  the bank announced plans to construct a new european headquarters at canary wharf london these plans were subsequently suspended in december  when the bank announced the purchase of a nearby existing office tower at  bank street for use as the european headquarters of its investment bank  bank street had originally been designated as the european headquarters of enron and was subsequently used as the headquarters of lehman brothers international europe the regional office is in london with offices in bournemouth glasgow and edinburgh for asset management private banking and investment financial dataedit financial data in  millions  year            revenue             net income            assets            employees            asset  liability assetliability ratio net income jpmorgan chase was the biggest bank at the end of  as an individual bank not including subsidiaries operationsedit earlier in  the company announced that by the use of supercomputers the time taken to assess risk had been greatly reduced from arriving at a conclusion within hours to what is now minutes the banking corporation uses for this calculation fieldprogrammable gate array technology historyedit the bank began operations in japan in  in australia during the later part of the n