est hedge fund in the united states the company was formed in  when chase manhattan corporation merged with jp morgan  co the jp morgan brand historically known as morgan is used by the investment banking asset management private banking private wealth management and treasury  securities services divisions fiduciary activity within private banking and private wealth management is done under the aegis of jpmorgan chase bank na—the actual trustee the chase brand is used for credit card services in the united states and canada the banks retail banking activities in the united states and commercial banking both the retail and commercial bank and the banks corporate headquarters are located at  park avenue in midtown manhattan new york city jpmorgan chase  co is considered to be a universal bank and a custodian bank as of  jpmorgan chase is one of the big four banks of the united states followed by bank of america citigroup and wells fargo contents  history  chase manhattan bank  chemical banking corporation  jp morgan  company  bank one corporation  bear stearns  washington mutual   settlement  other recent acquisitions  acquisition history  recent news  structure  jpmorgan europe ltd  financial data  operations  history  lobbying  controversies  conflicts of interest on investment research  enron  worldcom  jefferson county alabama  failure to comply with client money rules in the uk  mortgage overcharge of active military personnel  truth in lending act litigation  alleged manipulation of energy market  criminal investigation into obstruction of justice  sanctions violations  national mortgage settlement  speculative trading  mortgagebacked securities sales  sons and daughters hiring program  madoff fraud  corruption investigation in asia  september  cyberattack  alleged discrimination lawsuit  staff suicide  offices  credit derivatives  multibilliondollar trading loss  art collection  major sponsorships  notable former employees  business  politics and public service